testcase.name: ApplicationController .create should create a book in the database
ApplicationController .create with a bad request should return an error
ApplicationController .create duplicate request should create a book in the database and catch the duplicate request
ApplicationController .read should find a book in the database by id
ApplicationController .read with a bad request should return an error
ApplicationController .readAny should find a book in the database by name
ApplicationController .readAny should find a book in the database by numSales
ApplicationController .readAny with a bad request should return an error
ApplicationController .readAny with a bad field request should return an error
ApplicationController .update() should update a book in the database by id
ApplicationController .partialUpdate() should partially updates a field of a book in the database by id
ApplicationController .partialUpdate() with a request that does not find a book should should return a bad request and not change any books in the database
